Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
When I go to Page 12 of Pelvic MRI
Then 'Aggravation' radio button is enabled
And 'No change' radio button is enabled
And 'Improvement' radio button is enabled
And 'Detailed, after chemotherapy' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Detailed, after chemotherapy' radio button
Then 'TRG 1' radio button is enabled
And 'TRG 2' radio button is enabled
And 'TRG 3' radio button is enabled
And 'TRG 4' radio button is enabled
And 'TRG 5' radio button is enabled
